00:17:47.021 --> 00:17:49.595
Preta vidya?

00:17:49.605 --> 00:17:51.579
Oui, Preta vidya.

00:17:51.589 --> 00:17:54.085
Preta aussi en brésilien signifie "noir".

00:17:54.095 --> 00:17:55.317
Vraiment?

00:17:55.327 --> 00:17:56.682
En brésilien, c’est "noir".

00:17:56.692 --> 00:17:58.554
Mais "preta" signifie "mort".

00:17:58.564 --> 00:18:00.544
Mort, ah.

00:18:02.132 --> 00:18:07.020
